data.description: Ow, she's a brick house! Well put-together, everybody knows. This is how the story goes. She knows she got everything - an inviting entry displaying your formal dining room / media room & a living room with electric fireplace & built-ins for your decor. The kitchen has a side door for easy grocery transport & is as good as new with white cabinets, a gas stove & a nook for your breakfast table or even more cabinets. Notice all the closet space inside & the 476sqft 3-season porch(es) outside. The backyard is fully fenced for Fido & the 2 car garage just finished, with electrical & built-in storage. Don't forget about the 1,200 sq.ft of unfinished totally livable space in the basement! The home sits on a corner lot near all the new developments & is a hop, skip & a jump to I-75. She ain't holding nothing back!
